<P>__{(impatient)}
<D>__{what d'you got?}
<C>__{larry}
<D>__{i'm not supposed to tell. not until you've counted too. we're each supposed to make an independent count.}
<C>__{jim}
<D>__{you're kidding, right?}
<C>__{larry}
<D>__{i thought those were the rules, mr. mcallister. if they've changed in any way }
<C>__{jim}
<D>__{larry, we're not electing the fucking pope here. just tell me who won.}
